                <mxCell id="manager" value="BinaryManager&lt;br&gt;━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━&lt;br&gt;Core State Management&lt;br&gt;• instances: HashMap&lt;Instance ID, Instance&gt;&lt;br&gt;• service_to_instances: HashMap&lt;Service, Vec&lt;ID&gt;&gt; (1:N)&lt;br&gt;• check_and_reap(): 프로세스 감시&lt;br&gt;• spawn_process(): Child 생성&lt;br&gt;• history: VecDeque (max 1000)&lt;br&gt;• 비동기 JSONL 로깅 (mpsc)&lt;br&gt;• 자동 service_name 생성 (중복 허용)&lt;br&gt;• kyron::futures::sleep(1s)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#81c784;strokeColor=#2e7d32;fontStyle=1;fontSize=10;align=center;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="659" y="246" width="270" height="140" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
